// ============================================================================
// PLATFORM ANALYSIS (SuperAdmin AI Reports)
// ============================================================================

/// Stores AI-generated platform health analysis reports.
///
/// Generated on-demand by SUPER_ADMIN. The latest report is displayed
/// on the Platform Analytics page and survives page refreshes, navigation,
